results.title: Skull the Slayer (1975) #2
results.description: Man-on-the-run James Scully, along with a team of scientists, have flown straight into a Bermuda Triangle time-warp! How will Scully and his new comrades navigate a prehistoric world of dinosaurs? A discovery from an ancient alien race unleashes the power of Skull the Slayer. The transformation begins here, but will it also end? The saga of the man trapped 250 million years in the past continues!

results.title: Skull the Slayer (1975) #1
results.description: The saga of the Skull begins here! James Scully is a man down on his luck; a freed POW of Vietnam, he returns home to a life he barely recognizes. Scully’s brother has turned to drugs; his parents have died from grief believing their son to be dead, his wife has left him for another man. But when James ends up on the lam for a crime he didn’t commit, his downtrodden life takes a turn for the unexpected. Witness the birth of Skull the Slayer, a man trapped 250 million years in the past!
